      • registerUser

        public static boolean registerUser​(java.lang.String username,
                                   java.lang.String password,
                                   java.lang.String email)
        Handles registering of a new user with the desired username, password, and email. Hashes password using the generateSalt() and saltPassword() functions
        Parameters:
        username - String containing the desired username
        password - String containing the desired password
        email - String containing the desired email address
        Returns:
        boolean representing whether the registering of a new user was successful or not. Returns true if user was registered, and false if a user with either the same email or the same password already exists

        Returns:
